name: Collage01 (Lilith)
description:
Lilith (リリス Hebrew: נידה ,לילית: Lîlîṯ, Niddah) is designated as the Second Angel. Like Adam, Lilith is a Seed of Life, created by the First Ancestral Race billions of years ago. Thus, Lilith is actually a co-equal being to Adam. The other Angels are the progeny of Adam, but Lilith is the progenitor of the "Lilin": humans.
